title: #96: Media Mayhem with Ron Placone And Graham Elwood
description:
Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli welcomes from the Progressive Comedy Tour, Graham Elwood and Ron Placone, to discuss.....
1) Operation Mockingbird
2)Data Mining
3)Astroturfing
4)Pop Culture Psyops
Thank you so much for your support.
